original_title: 鈴木香音 バースデーイベント ～音の香りゆく15祭～
overview: Fanclub event by Morning Musume. 9th generation members Ikuta Erina and Suzuki Kanon and 10th generation member Sato Masaki. The event celebrates Suzuki Kanon's 15th birthday as well and was held at Tokyo FM Hall.
title: Suzuki Kanon Birthday Event ~Oto no Kaori Yuku 15sai~
